---
title: Basil Pesto Chicken & Roast Pumpkin Risoni with Chilli Pangrattato & Feta Cheese
description: Risoni – the clever pasta that looks like rice – is the ideal ingredient in this warm bowl. With pumpkin and courgette, this dinner
filled with goodness gets the welcome addition of feta cheese and basil pesto to really raise the flavour stakes.

